Description: Global sensitivity analysis (GSA) for physiologically based
    pharmacokinetic (PBPK) models built in PK-Sim/MoBi. 
    Provides correlation-aware, distribution-based Monte Carlo designs and a 
    suite of variance-based and moment-independent sensitivity estimators. 
    Sensitivity can be computed on scalar PK parameters (AUC, Cmax, ...) and on 
    the full concentration-time profile. The GSA engine is model-agnostic.
    ospsuite models have built-in integration.
